data.title: Alliance of Hope for Suicide Loss Survivors
data.meta_description: Our memorial wall is an online space to remember the lives of loved ones. Connect with other survivors of suicide loss with Alliance of Hope.
data.meta_site_name: Alliance of Hope for Suicide Loss Survivors
data.text:
In a field of roses, you are a beautiful smiling sunflower with a heart of gold.

Anon

You are my soulmate, my best friend, and my forever after.

LeAnn

I know everything has a beginning and ending. Let’s be clear my love for you will never end.

Pops

The legacy of love and life that he and I shared together is so much bigger than his death. His life meant – and means so much more than that moment in time where it ended.

In Shock

God grant me the serenity to accept the things I cannot change, the courage to change the things I can, and the wisdom to know the difference.

Reinhold Niebuhr

The winds of healing sift through the windows. Where pain and sorrow once thrived, refreshing peace now lives. The threads between are a tapestry of shared wounds and holy moments.

Iris Bolton

Ring the bells that still can ring. Forget your perfect offering. There is a crack, a crack in everything. That’s how the light gets in.

Leonard Cohen

The world is a little darker without you in it.

Forever Your Loving Daughter

We miss your funny sayings, stories told and retold, how proud your grandchildren made you, and your amazingly beautiful piano playing.

Laurie E

For as long as we live

they too shall live

for they are now a part of us

as we remember them.

Jewish Prayer

I can’t carry you in my arms but I can carry your legacy and how I live my life.

Unknown

May the everlasting love of God heal your deepest wounds and bring you peace everlasting. Love you always and forever,

Mom

Part of our legacy will be telling our loved one’s story, the good and the bad. We are the truth bearers now, the ones who can keep their memories alive and bring a cautionary tale to others.

SadNGeorgia

Son, wherever you are, my love will find you. Missing you dearly.

Mom

To my awesome dad, I just want you to know that you are my hero.

Baby Girl

But tell me, did the wind sweep you off your feet? Did you finally get the chance to dance along the light of day and head back to the Milky Way?

Train

The first star I set my eyes on, I know that it’s you shining bright above me.

Amy

Silently, one by one, in the infinite meadows of heaven,

Blossomed the lovely stars, the forget-me-nots of the angels.

Henry Wadsworth Longfellow

I will forever be your sunshine and you will forever be in my heart ♥

Christine

Your absence has gone through me like thread through a needle. Everything I do is stitched with its color.

WS Merwin

You were my cool aunt. Take me on one more drive, let’s go see the sunset and buy some iced tea. Please wait for me wherever you are.

Wren

If you’re sad, mad, or scared, close your eyes and take a deep breath. I’ll be right there with you.

Darla

I pray that God cradles you in his arms while you rest in eternal peace.

Mom

Talk not of my departure with sighs in your hearts;

Close your eyes and you will see me with you forevermore.

Kahlil Gibran

Right now, my beautiful boy is walking through the Pearly Gates of Heaven. He is walking straight up to Saint Peter with an extended hand and saying: Hi! My name is Pat.

Steve Shannon

Fly high my precious baby,

and though I wish that you could stay.

I know you are finally at peace,

and I will see you again someday.

WESLIE’S MOMMY

You have the most beautiful heart I will ever know.

Omayma

A man’s reach should exceed his grasp, to achieve anything worthwhile, a person should attempt even those things that may turn out to be impossible.

Robert Browning

The fierce, never-ending love that I feel for my son is the very thing that sustains me every day.

Betsy4

He was first to be there with a warm hug, a smile, or some off-the-wall joke or one-liner that would instantly raise our spirits. That’s who my son was.

Steve

Your life and death won’t be without meaning. … If even one life can be saved from telling our story, then the ripples of your legacy, your life and even your loss will be without end.

Deborah Greene

There Are Some Who Bring A Light So Great To The World, That Even After They Have Gone, The Light Remains.

Unknown

Whatever we were to each other, that we are still.

Henry Scott-Holland

I was still the boy on your shoulders, and when you disappeared, I fell.

Mat

I thought of you today

I thought about you yesterday and days before that too.

I think of you in silence,

I often speak your name.

Unknown

Today, my dear daughter, I feel and honor all of my emotions. I miss you.

Mom

Hope you are okay. Hope I see you again. In a better place. I hope.

NM

I see you everywhere, in the stars, in the river.

To me you’re everything that exists; the reality of everything.

Virginia Woolf

You are there. I am here. Worlds separate us. … Yet I say your name, and waves of light wash to me silently from your heart.

Rumi

I love you so much and will continue on your legacy. Keep sending me signs. 🦋

Madeline

Grief has no calendar; our soul feels her absence as deeply today as when we first lost her tender embrace.

Unknown

I could not follow you to Viet Nam. I cannot follow you now. Although at times I want to. … I will pick up your missions of P.O.W. and M.I.A. And help honor you. I wish you would have stayed.

Sharon, Your Loving Sis

We truly miss you, more than you could ever fathom.

Amanda

I will forever miss you. I need you every second of everyday.

Lisa

When I go

don’t learn to live without me

just learn to look for me in the moments.

I will be there.

Donna Ashworth

I was forever changed when you came into my life, and forever changed again when you left.

Alice

I’ll miss you until the day we meet again in heaven 🙏❤️

Rebecca

Love you for eternity, my sweet gem.

Mom

Your loss is immeasurable. But so is the depth of the love you leave behind.

Alison

He was a smart and loving individual who always looked after the ones he loved. … He was a leader, a problem solver, a broken angel, and one of a kind.

Polo PTB
